brightness.shell: Trimean brightness and interquartile (difference between quartiles) of shell
brightness.shell center: Trimean brightness and interquartile (difference between quartiles) of shell center
brightness.background: Trimean brightness and interquartile (difference between quartiles) of background

arcs.Y: (list) [arcsec] Offsets from star perpendicular to axis of shell points
arcs.R: (list) [arcsec] Radii of shell points from star
arcs.x: (list) [arcsec] RA offsets from star of shell points
arcs.y: (list) [arcsec] Dec offsets from star of shell points
arcs.X: (list) [arcsec] Offsets from star parallel to axis of shell points
arcs.theta: (list) [deg] Angle from axis of shell points

star.D: [arcsec] Distance of th^1 C from source
star.PA: [deg] Position Angle of th^1 C from source
star.id: Source identifier deduced from region filename

thickness.h0: Shell thickness on axis: h0 = R0(outer) - R0(inner)
